Comment: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:47.04,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}As the memories fade away
Comment: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:52.37,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}The lives of those who weren’t saved
Comment: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:57.63,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}Regret and torment has come to stay
Comment: 0,0:21:58.30,0:22:02.38,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}Hopelessly leading us astray
Comment: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:10.06,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}On a journey to find some kind of reason
Comment: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:14.98,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}The army’s weight is only crumbling
Comment: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:19.53,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}Haunted by the look of those who we’ve left behind
Comment: 0,0:22:19.53,0:22:24.74,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}Close your eyes, try to leave the shame behind
Comment: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:30.04,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}Who will stay to lend a helping hand
Comment: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:35.17,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}When death is knocking at the door
Comment: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:40.51,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}Who will fight alone for what is right
Comment: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:45.18,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}For the ones who were left behind
Comment: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:48.14,ED_EN_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}Those who were left behind
Comment: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:47.04,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}当记忆渐渐模糊
Comment: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:52.37,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}那些未被挽救的生命
Comment: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:57.63,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}后悔与折磨长留心中
Comment: 0,0:21:58.30,0:22:02.38,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}使我们绝望迷失
Comment: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:10.06,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}在寻找理由的旅途之中
Comment: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:14.98,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}当队伍开始分崩离析
Comment: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:19.53,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}被抛弃之人的面庞挥之不去
Comment: 0,0:22:19.53,0:22:24.74,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}闭上眼睛想忘记愧疚
Comment: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:30.04,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}谁会留下伸出援手
Comment: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:35.17,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}当死亡已经近在咫尺
Comment: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:40.51,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}谁会独自战斗追寻正义
Comment: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:45.18,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}为那些被抛弃的人们
Comment: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:48.14,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,720)\blur2}那些被抛弃的人们
